===Etymology===
From Old Galician and {{inh|gl|roa-opt|jogar}}, from {{inh|gl|la|ioco|iocāre}}, collateral form of {{m|la|ioco|iocārī}}. Compare {{cog|ast|xugar}}, {{cog|pt|jogar}}, {{cog|es|jugar}}.
